- Implement Tier-1: Opus GO (empirical exploit probes) but codex+gemini BLOCK on a verified windows-compile regression (syscall.O_NOFOLLOW undefined on GOOS=windows; HEAD compiled before) → fixed with build-tagged nofollowFlag + the windows-skip nit; codex+gemini round-2 GO → UNANIMOUS.
